## Examples

<span data-ttu-id="88d22-239">Dieses Beispiel ruft den ReceiveSynchronously-Wert ab.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="88d22-239">This example gets the ReceiveSynchronously value.</span></span>

